"" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 photo avatar-default" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Gonzalo Tello"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/gonzalo-tello/">View all articles by Gonzalo Tello</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2010/08/macerata-opera-festival-2010juditha-triumphans-e-attila/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Macerata Opera Festival 2010:&#8221;Juditha Triumphans&#8221; e &#8220;Attila&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2010/08/vincente-martin-y-soler-1754-1806il-burbero-di-buon-cuore/" rel="next">Vincente Martn y Soler (1754 &#8211; 1806):&#8221;Il burbero di buon cuore&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2010/08/lima-teatro-seguracavalleria-rusticana-e-pagliacci/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sar pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="require